### "Ganja Burn"

"Ganja Burn" is a track that surfaced on [Nicki Minaj](/Nicki_Minaj)'s fourth studio album, [Queen](/Queen_(Nicki_Minaj_album)), released in the year 2018. This song, officially dropped on August 10, 2018, was a collaborative effort in its creation. The songwriting credits list [Onika Maraj](/Nicki_Minaj) herself, alongside Jairus Mozee and Jeremy Reid. The production, handled by Reid, gave the song its distinct soundscape.

The track was recorded across several studios, each contributing to its final polish: Glenwood Place Studios in [Burbank, California](/Burbank,_California), [Larrabee Sound Studios](/Larrabee_Sound_Studios) in [North Hollywood, California](/North_Hollywood,_California), and the mastering was finalized at Chris Athens Masters in [Austin, Texas](/Austin,_Texas).

**Genre:** [Reggae fusion](/Reggae_fusion), [hip hop](/Hip_hop)
**Length:** 4:54
**Label:** [Young Money](/Young_Money_Entertainment), [Cash Money](/Cash_Money_Records)
**Songwriter:** [Onika Maraj](/Nicki_Minaj)
**Producer:** Jeremy Reid

A visual component was also created for the song; the [music video](/Music_video) for "Ganja Burn" can be found on [YouTube](/YouTube_video_(identifier)).

